{"tid":2226634,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"老闆俾到員工d咩？","createTime":"2020-10-02T06:38:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T14:16:33.000Z","uid":190284,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"630d78a35f3640ced6fd7b5ce58e57794c68b797","tid":2226634,"uid":190284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T06:38:26.000Z","msg":"請指教<br />\n謝謝"},{"pid":"5660736bf4f8d9b8309f1982509c05679c9e8397","tid":2226634,"uid":162558,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T06:38:48.000Z","msg":"你老尾又係&quot;fernando&quot;你條柒頭<br />\n成撚日請人指教<br />\n不如你改名叫&quot;fer-don't know&quot;算吧啦<br />\n<br />\n屌你老味, 呢啲咪低質素Post囉，<br />\n成撚日問人指教指教，乜柒都唔Provide俾大家討論<br />\n有咩好指教啫? 屌你十足十 香土咁撚樣, 開撚埋,無討論價值嘅話題<br />\n自己立場又唔講下,打撚完個題目就拍拍屁股走人,<br />\n你不如唔撚好打[請指教]. 就噉話[如題] 咪算柒數囉<br />\n係都貼下圖呀, 屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n淨係請人指教, 成個戇鳩仔<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母fer-don't know<br />\n你條撚皮係唔撚係條條問題都話答唔到你㗎柒頭<br />\n<br />\n答到又繼續推舊post又打5P字<br />\n答唔到又當人冇到所以唔鬼Contribute<br />\n<br />\n成日咁撚得閒上嚟連登出埋啲低質素Post鳩噏問人指教<br />\n不如用啲時間去進修下 醫下你個死人腦好過啦<br />\n<br />\n最後補多次<br />\nfernando我屌你老母"},{"pid":"4f3abd8e46fb8305459d7fca660f063efaa60081","tid":2226634,"uid":162558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T06:39:03.000Z","msg":"請指插伯母，射射"},{"pid":"0760deb75e91d56d1f0d61daca226da153bd077a","tid":2226634,"uid":311837,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T06:39:19.000Z","msg":"錢"},{"pid":"03102a39584845c38bc2a22b315a9ee312dc7dbf","tid":2226634,"uid":190284,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"0760deb75e91d56d1f0d61daca226da153bd077a","tid":2226634,"uid":311837,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T06:39:19.000Z","msg":"錢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T06:42:05.000Z","msg":"點解俾既錢少過工作量<br />\n點解俾錢時又拖<br />\n（甚至唔俾）"},{"pid":"62df9e4290bb5808ce4aa9d6e5644e7bd273524d","tid":2226634,"uid":176802,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T06:45:29.000Z","msg"